	"system": {
		"description": "<p>When you cast a spell of 1st level or higher that deals fire damage, you can spend 1 sorcery point to gain temporary hit points equal to your Charisma modifier + the spell’s level.</p><p>Once per long rest, when you drop to 0 HP, you can instead remain at 1 HP and immediately emit a 5-foot burst explosion. Any creature in range must make a Dexterity Saving Throw (Spell save DC) or take fire damage equal to your sorcerer level, and half on a success.</p>",
